News Releases, Media Advisories

April 23, 2003

ATTENTION WIRE SERVICES, DAYBOOK EDITORS:
FINAL AUDIT REPORT ON
THE DEMOCRATIC PARTY OF WISCONSIN FEDERAL ACCOUNT
The Federal Election Commission has made available the final audit report on the Democratic Party of Wisconsin Federal Account. This audit covers the period of January 1, 1999 through December 31, 2000.

Contact: FEC Press Office (202) 694-1220, 999 E Street, NW
title: FEC Releases Final Audit Report on Democratic Party of Wisconsin Federal Account
